; Coverage test for post.cc
; Tests cost, calculated, cost_calculated, and use_direct_amount accessors.
; The first posting has an explicit cost (@ price).
; The second posting is auto-calculated (POST_CALCULATED flag).

2024/03/01 Purchase
    Expenses:Food     100 EUR @ $1.10
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(cost) %(calculated) %(cost_calculated) %(use_direct_amount)\n"
$110 false false false
$-110 true false false
end test
